  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/147d2ca452f006d18ba5915c47ef873c.avif?t=1761920924\" width=600 height=246 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The time has come for a new era of space exploration. We can detect and use <strong>warp portals</strong> to travel to other galaxies. But it allowed other space dwellers to detect us...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/87f9c7fedd05d5cf2095e87158d7b79b.poster.avif?t=1761920924\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/87f9c7fedd05d5cf2095e87158d7b79b.webm?t=1761920924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/87f9c7fedd05d5cf2095e87158d7b79b.mp4?t=1761920924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...and not all contacts are going to be peaceful. Especially, if you are a member of <strong>Cosmo Riders guild</strong> who pays bounty for <strong>capturing outposts and disassembling ships</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/5b3276e882fd579591df5b8e527d21f8.poster.avif?t=1761920924\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/5b3276e882fd579591df5b8e527d21f8.webm?t=1761920924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/5b3276e882fd579591df5b8e527d21f8.mp4?t=1761920924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Advance</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel through galaxies and solar systems during Expedition where each stage may have different <strong>conditions and events</strong>(from destructible asteroids to flying comets).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/10c1d01254bbe82995bf83ddb3b364a5.poster.avif?t=1761920924\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/10c1d01254bbe82995bf83ddb3b364a5.webm?t=1761920924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/10c1d01254bbe82995bf83ddb3b364a5.mp4?t=1761920924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Research</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Research new weapons, modules and modifications between Expeditions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/26d283b30a2d9ecbc454aadc0082d5c6.poster.avif?t=1761920924\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/26d283b30a2d9ecbc454aadc0082d5c6.webm?t=1761920924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/26d283b30a2d9ecbc454aadc0082d5c6.mp4?t=1761920924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Improve</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade Ship during Expedition: install researched weapons, modules, modifications. Change basic aspects (attributes).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/2585ebfdacb93a3f382ee990290febd9.webp?t=1761920924\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/2585ebfdacb93a3f382ee990290febd9.poster.avif?t=1761920924\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=338 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deal</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete Contracts to unlock new Research Tiers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/93ab10ea1d30cb7d6a1becb9f575eb65.avif?t=1761920924\" width=600 height=348 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Conquer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemy waves, extract cargo and components and jump into warp-portal to next stage. Enemies may also use different weapons and modules, but they can be shot-off during fight (node-based destruction).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/10cfa7eeffdcb337e89d673ab749be01.poster.avif?t=1761920924\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/10cfa7eeffdcb337e89d673ab749be01.webm?t=1761920924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/10cfa7eeffdcb337e89d673ab749be01.mp4?t=1761920924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/d6a0adc5a535204823ff49eb7160b7bc.poster.avif?t=1761920924\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/d6a0adc5a535204823ff49eb7160b7bc.webm?t=1761920924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/d6a0adc5a535204823ff49eb7160b7bc.mp4?t=1761920924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FAQ</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Run duration</strong>: one expedition takes near 1 hour, with ~20 minutes per each phase. Also progress is saved each ~1-3 minutes, the expedition can be postponed almost any time.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Total playtime</strong>: 18 Galaxies with unique conditions and 6 difficulties (configured per galaxy). It will take at least 20 hours to beat all galaxies at one difficulty level. All progress can be reset after completing all galaxies (statistics is kept).  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Meta-progression / Boosters</strong>: researched items appear during run(Expedition). Researched items can be crafted before Expedition start. Permanent bonus Attribute point is obtained after completing Galaxy. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ship builds</strong> (gameplay styles): 3 archetypes can be defined for now: ranger-with-focus-on-weapons, ranger-with-focus-on-modules and melee-hyper-boost-rammer. And ship modification system is flexible enough to combine different styles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Randomness</strong>: it is possible to predefine ~50% of build before Expedition starts. Other 50% are choices done during Expedition.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2539090/extras/20e403e7df7470d1217736e0dc075cea.avif?t=1761920924\" width=600 height=246 /></span></p>",
